# Copy this file to `.dev.vars` in this folder (same directory as wrangler.toml).
# Wrangler loads `.dev.vars` when you run `npm run dev` here — it does NOT use
# `wrangler secret put` values for local dev.
#
#   cp .dev.vars.example .dev.vars
#
# Rules (if Resend says "API key is invalid", check these):
# - One line: RESEND_API_KEY=re_xxxxxxxx  (no spaces around =)
# - No double quotes around the value unless you really want them stripped
# - Do not put a comment on the same line as the key
# - Paste ONLY the key from https://resend.com/api-keys — not "Bearer re_..."
#
# Test the key without running the Worker:
#   npm run verify-resend

RESEND_API_KEY=re_paste_your_key_here
